            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C) [In nomine sanctae et individue Trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName> divina
                        favente clemencia <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si sacris et
                        venerabilibus locis temporale subsidium conferimus, id nobis ad aeterne
                        remunerationis praemium proficere nequaquam ambigimus. Idcirco noverit
                        omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesie nostrorumque] presentium scilicet [ac
                        futuroruin industria,] <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Queen #legallyRecognisedUnionWith" ref="#people/155"
                            >Berchtilam</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen #legallyRecognisedUnionWith">dilectissi[mam coniugem
                            nostrique regni co]nsortem</rs> supplici[ter nostram exorasse <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">clemenciam</rs>,] quatenus pro Dei amore et remedio
                        animae nostrae omnia quicquid regiae parti <rs key="#Castle">in castro
                            </rs><orgName key="#Gai #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/136"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterii Sanctae Dei genetricis virginis
                                Mariae</rs> scito <placeName key="#Gai #Monasteries"
                                ref="#places/564"><rs key="#Gai">in Gaio
                        </rs></placeName></orgName>pertinere dinnoscitur, <rs key="#Teloneum"
                            >theloneum </rs>videlicet <rs key="#Districtio">cum omnibus
                            districtionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fluvial_transport #Local_markets #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            > ripaticum, cum universis mercationibus</rs> seu et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">palificturam</rs>, prout
                            dudum<geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/124">
                            <rs key="#Comitatus">ad partem Veronensium commitatus</rs></geogName>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Ports #Local_markets"
                            ref="#places/572"><rs
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Castle #Ports #Local_markets"
                                >in Ruviscello </rs></placeName>reddebantur, nec non et <rs
                            key="#Fish #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">quandam postam</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rivers">in Gavo fluvio</rs> qui nominatur Pontarla, sive <rs
                            key="#Islands #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >quandam insulam</rs> scitam <rs key="#Rivers">in alveo Atesis</rs> quae
                            <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Islands #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Brandigum</placeName> dicitur prefato monasterio, cui in presenti
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/352">Rodibertus</persName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots">abba</rs> preesse dinosscitur, <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure proprietario </rs>per hoc
                        [nostrum regale] preceptum modis omnibus concedere dignaremur. Nos vero
                        dignis eius petitionibus assensum prebentes, theloneum, mercationes,
                        ripaticum, palificturam et cunctas districtiones seu quicquid inibi nostrae
                        regiae parti pertinere videtur, prout olim ad partem comitis Veronensis in
                        Ruviscello solvebatur, prenominato monasterio Sanctae virginis Mariae sito
                        Gaio concedimus et largimur usque in perpetuum, seu et prenominatam postam
                        Pontarla, nec non et prelibatam insulam ex integro perpetualiter ac nostrae
                        auctoritatis inscriptione suprataxato monasterio habenda, tenenda ac
                        possidenda concedimus et largimur, et de nostro iure ac dominio in eius ius
                        atque dominium omnino transfund[i]mus et donamus, quatenus omnia superius
                        conprehensa pars prefati monasterii ad sua iura in omnibus vindicet atque
                        nullo contradicente possideat. Quod si etiam <placeName
                            key="#Ports #Local_markets" ref="#places/572"><rs
                                key="#Castle #Ports #Local_markets">Rovescellus
                        </rs></placeName>fuerit aliquando recup[e]ratus, dari haec omnia ad
                        proprietatem et iura prelibati monasterii precipimus atque nostra regia
                        auctoritate decernimus. Contra quod nostrae autoritatis seu concessionis
                        preceptum si quis insurgere temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, medietatem <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">camerae nostrae</rs> et medietatem pr[e]dicto
                        Rodiberto abbati suisque successoribus. Quod ut verius credatur et
                        dililgentius ab omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes anuli nostri
                        inpressione acsignari precepimu[s.] Signum domnus (MF) Berengarii
                        serenissimi regis. <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/619">Ambrosius
                            </persName><rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchaplain #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi </persName><rs
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops">episcopi et archicancellarii
                        </rs>recognovi et subscripsi. (SR) (SI D) Data kal. aug., anno dominicae
                        incarnationis .DCCCCV., domni vero Berengarii sererenissimi regis .XVIII.,
                        indictione .VIII. Actum <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention" ref="#places/364"
                                ><rs key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                            >Tulles</rs></placeName>. in Christi nomine feliciter, amen.</ab>
         
                </div>
